    {
      "chinese": "台灣原住民族共有16族。泰雅族、賽夏族、布農族、鄒族、邵族、排灣族、魯凱族、卑南族、阿美族、達悟族、噶瑪蘭族、太魯閣族、撒奇萊雅族、賽德克族、拉阿魯哇族及卡那卡那富族。",
      "ab": "Ita Seediq tnpusu bale Taywan hini, snpegan daha we 16 klegan ka Yencuming. So ka Tayal, Saysiyat, Bunun, Cou, Thau, Paywan, Rukai, Puyuma, Amis, Tao, Kavalan, Truku, Sakizaya, Seediq, Saaruwa ma Kanakanavu.",
